  "title": "Class 4/ Class 5 Driver cum Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Ferry workers from to and from work site.</li>\n  <li>Supervise worker</li>\n  <li>Operate lorry crane</li>\n  <li>Supervise worker</li>\n  <li>Report to Project Manager</li>\n  <li>Deliver documents or materials to required destinations.</li>\n  <li>Loading and unloading of materials from the vehicle.</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily checks to ensure that the vehicle is in good and safe condition.</li>\n  <li>Keep vehicle clean and regular maintenance on vehicle.</li>\n  <li>Drive in safety manner at all times and adhering to traffic rules and regulations stated in the road traffic.</li>\n  <li>Attend to other ad hoc duties instructed by immediate superior.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3/Class 4/Class 5 driver with good driving records.</li>\n  <li>WSQ Operate Lorry Crane Certificate</li>\n  <li>Possess a positive attitude, meticulous and organised</li>\n  <li>Willing to learn, independent and self-motivated</li>\n  <li>At least 1 years working experience</li>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least Primary/Secondary School/\"O\" Level</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Singapore road.</li>\n  <li>Able to handle moderately heavy goods.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude to work independently as a team player.</li>\n  <li>Singaporean only.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p>\n<p>· 5.5/6 days work per week</p>\n<p>· Working Hours: 8am to 7pm</p>",
